 Foxfingers flew through Egypt observing the wildlife as he went. 
Shakes lizards, bugs, vultures, all seemed to have a natural part in 
this world. suddenly he realized the wildlife had disapeared. he was 
in a spot where they seemed to be avoiding. There was definately 
something wrong here and it had Predacon written all over it. He knew 
he had to be near a base. he just moved north hoping that it was the 
right direction to be moving away from the base.
